A ci-cd.yml defines how the pipeline operates with:
workflow name: a label to identify the pipeline
triggering events: specify actions to trigger the workflow
jobs: define the tasks (like building or testing)
permissions: grant appropriate access levels to resources in repo

sample:

name: sample-pipeline
on:
  push:
    branches:
      - main
jobs:
  build:
    runs-on: ubuntu-latest
    steps:
      - name: checkout code
        uses: actions/checkout@v3